1
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:16,360
Oh.

2
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:17,760
Boss.

3
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,240
Boss.

4
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:22,160
Why are you up so early?

5
00:00:22,240 --> 00:00:24,480
It's only 5.30.

6
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:28,360
And your meds shouldn't have worn off yet.
You can go back to sleep.

7
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,240
That's right.

8
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,720
We're still okay, boss.

9
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:32,640
No, thanks.

10
00:00:33,040 --> 00:00:34,040
I'm up.

11
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,600
You guys can go home and rest.

12
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:41,160
Being an iron woman again.

13
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,400
Oh, anyway...

14
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:48,040
Cute outfit.

15
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,080
Kind of innocent.

16
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:55,920
Innocent, right?

17
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,520
What about Ms. Ayla?

18
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,080
Still asleep, right?

19
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,520
Yes.

20
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:09,840
She went to bed at almost three in the morning.

21
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:12,440
Okay.

22
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,000
-Stop it.
-Ya.

23
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:28,840
Boss, are you really okay?

24
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,840
It's far from my heart.

25
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,680
Your wound is,

26
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:45,520
but somehow I feel like
there's someone kind of close to your heart.

27
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,520
Go already.

28
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,920
You're ridiculous.

29
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,760
Ridiculous.

30
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:57,520
I mean you're all ridiculous.

31
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,800
Can you go back to work?

32
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,240
Will I get that bike's info today?

33
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,120
You'll get it by noon, boss.

34
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:06,960
Good.

35
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,720
Well,

36
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,199
why are you still here?

37
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,080
Go back to work.

38
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,160
Well, let's pack up.

39
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,080
Why did you bring this? It's huge.

40
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,120
Tawan.

41
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,120
How do you feel?

42
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,640
It's better.

43
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,400
I'm fine now.

44
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,880
Is there something wrong?

45
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,960
I...

46
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,320
want to terminate your contract.

47
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,360
May I ask why?

48
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:08,280
I'm sure my company hasn't made a mistake.

49
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:12,160
Or did those three offend you in some way?

50
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:13,800
Not at all.

51
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,360
They were wonderful.

52
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,760
And your company takes great care of me.

53
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,680
I'm not unhappy with anything.

54
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:28,040
And I'm so glad to have you around taking care of me.

55
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:33,520
But I don't want
what happened yesterday to happen again.

56
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,400
You got hurt because of me.

57
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,760
I was the reason.

58
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:44,400
Someone tried to hurt me,
but why did you have to get hurt?

59
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:48,320
Then I'm declining your request.

60
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:53,200
My contract cannot be terminated for that reason.

61
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,920
Then...

62
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,280
I'll buy out your contract in full.

63
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,360
Your company won't have to pay anything.

64
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,560
I don't care about that stuff.

65
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:08,880
Your safety is paramount right now.

66
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,080
The situation you're in

67
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:16,000
is too dangerous for me to let go.

68
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:24,400
Your life is now my duty and responsibility.

69
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:31,720
But if you're unhappy with how I work,

70
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,000
I'm willing to walk away.

71
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:58,720
I'm sure there are other companies
that can take on this duty better.
